sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Usuario
    participant PWA as User PWA
    participant Keycloak as Keycloak
    participant Gateway as API Gateway (KrakenD)
    participant PwaBff as PWA BFF
    participant Supabase as Supabase
    participant R2 as Cloudflare R2

    User->>PWA: Abre la PWA
    PWA->>Keycloak: Solicita autenticacion
    Keycloak-->>PWA: Retorna access token
    PWA->>Gateway: Solicita conteo y video
    Gateway->>Keycloak: Valida access token
    Keycloak-->>Gateway: Token valido
    Gateway->>PwaBff: Enruta solicitud PWA
    PwaBff->>Supabase: Consulta conteo de ovejas
    Supabase-->>PwaBff: Retorna datos de conteo
    PwaBff->>R2: Consulta video procesado
    R2-->>PwaBff: Retorna referencia del video
    PwaBff-->>Gateway: Retorna datos consolidados
    Gateway-->>PWA: Retorna conteo y video
    PWA-->>User: Muestra monitoreo de la finca
